thread.title: Authorities Investigate Shooting Incident Outside NSA Campus in Maryland

author: Scott Calvert
title: Authorities Investigate Shooting Incident Outside NSA Campus in Maryland
text:
Authorities were investigating a shooting incident Wednesday morning outside the National Security Agency headquarters complex at Fort Meade, Md.
The Federal Bureau of Investigation ruled out terrorism.
